When user types name of a "consola" in search
Then is redirected to the videogames section
And user selects "Xbox One S 1TB"
And user selects add to bag and increases to two products
And user selects extended "2 Años $ 32.990"
Then is redirected to the summary of your order
And user selects go purchase
And user chooses dispatch options "REGION METROPOLITANA" and "SANTIAGO CENTRO"
And user chooses option pick up purchase
And user selects store and continue
And user selects "Débito y efectivo" method
Then user completes information "juan""perez""juan.perez@gmail.com""269961414""965330978" and reserves the purchase
